{"tid":460082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雷鼎鳴稱不會「支爆」：內地叫雞都可手機付款 生活方便過香港","createTime":"2017-11-06T10:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T10:57:16.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2a820c1faab90cc6b75cc09fc36aa23c5e6c68","tid":460082,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"香港科技大學經濟系前系主任及榮休教授雷鼎鳴今日出席以「國家與香港」為題的研討會指，香港部分人認為國家經濟會冧，支持港獨，有人甚至以「支爆」形容國家面臨的危機，但他認為內地經濟不會爆煲。<br />\n<br />\n雷鼎鳴指，在內地捐錢給乞丐、「叫雞」也可以透過手機付款，來說明內地生活十分方便，遠超香港，「有事實擺喺度，你就算冇掌握數據，你走去大陸行吓啦，你點見到（經濟）有咩會冧，科技上面嘅進步，學術論文嘅增長，大陸生活程度方便過香港，你畀錢乞兒，都可以攞部手機出嚟照一照，我識得朋友叫雞（召妓）嘅，佢話叫雞都可以拎部手機出嚟照，香港呢啲嘢仲未做得到」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171106/57425269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171106%2F57425269&d=LGXF8pnRWKgDDRU%2FAc5FZ0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=160e4cf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171106%2F57425269&h=a1a89570\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171106/57425269</a>"},{"pid":"d0a11e8f092b4cb9e674b29cb9401d4787548da9","tid":460082,"uid":45914,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e49221e7155c68cd11e7c66a6333224338a1274d","tid":460082,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"到時掃黃check record就拉得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb232437a30a6ff479ae0166ea27d955caeb6154","tid":460082,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:44:42.000Z","msg":"雷Sir mark 開小紅定小翠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c53947e99f5ee98ae3e601f3016a6eb8706c514","tid":460082,"uid":25869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10: